# Vercel upload ignore. This OVERRIDES .gitignore for deploys.
#
# CRITICAL: do NOT use a bare `node_modules` pattern here. Expo's web export
# writes hashed font/image assets under paths like
#   artifacts/mobile/web-dist/assets/__node_modules/.pnpm/<pkg>/node_modules/.../Ionicons.ttf
# A bare `node_modules` rule matches that deep segment and drops the fonts from
# the upload, so Vercel serves index.html for .ttf requests → icon boxes.
# Instead, ignore ONLY the dependency node_modules dirs by anchored path.
.git
.vercel
.env
.env.*
_api-bundle.cjs
artifacts/mobile/web-dist

/node_modules
/artifacts/*/node_modules
/lib/*/node_modules
/scripts/node_modules
